  "texts": [
    "IntroductionIn traffic scenarios, object detection is the most critical task for autonomous driving because a comprehensive understanding of the environment is crucial for driving control.",
    "In addition, object detection is an important research branch in the field of computer vision and the basis for object recognition and tracking.",
    "Object detection consists of two aspects: one is to classify the object (object classification), and the other is to determine the position of the object in the scene (object localization).",
    "Over the past few decades, research in autonomous driving systems has become increasingly important.",
    "Object detection methods are widely used in systems such as vehicle detection, pedestrian detection, traffic light detection, and traffic sign detection."
  ],
